name: Julia Oborina
description: If you want to know what a real lady is talk to me and you’ll be pleasantly surprised. I`m sure You will find me always full of energy, creative, active girl, adoring her job, friends and loving her family Yes, I treasure moments I spend with my family but at the same time, I long for the moment all tenderness, kindness and love of my heart I share with my beloved. Deep inside I wish my man to cherish my inner world and personality more than my body. Wish us both to fall in love with our hearts and souls Yes, I indeed dream of such a family, as in the one where mutual love, passion, harmony lives.
